        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="浅入浅出二分法">浅入浅出“二分法”</h1>
<blockquote>
<p>[!CAUTION]</p>
<p>注意！本文章只介绍笔者在学习二分法时所遇到的坑点，以昭示后人别重蹈覆辙，只适合新手学习，不适合神犇进阶！</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="q1什么是二分法">Q1：什么是二分法？</h2>
<p>二分法是解决“<strong>非线性函数（线性函数也行）的解</strong>”时的一种高效算法（还有三分、退火等奇奇怪怪的算法解决该算法难以解决的问题）</p>
<p>简单来说就是折半查找（类似递推）</p>
<h2 id="q2何时使用二分法二分法的原理">Q2：何时使用二分法？二分法的原理？</h2>
<p>总的来说，在求解 <strong>单调不减或单调不增的函数的解时使用</strong>，在实际解决背景中，有 “<strong>最大值最小化    最小值最大化</strong>”等找在具有确定定义域<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>[</mo><mi>a</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">[a,b]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="mclose">]</span></span></span></span>的函数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 时</p>
<p>满足<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi>R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">且</mi><mi>m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">已</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">知</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)=m(m\in R且m已知)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">且</span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">已</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">知</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>的x值（<s>用不太严谨的话就是找一有序区间内的某个元素的位置</s>）</p>
<p>如图，我们想要找<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">[0,4]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mclose">]</span></span></span></span>中<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f(x)=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>​时自变量的值<br>
<img src="https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/67137bedd29ded1a8c7c81d6.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>[!NOTE]</p>
<p>笔者在这里强调了对应法则、区间及目标函数值，这是二分法使用的三个前提条件</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
